findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeAccount() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply respectively. These functions can be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change critical parameters and add/remove bots when the owner is not renounced.
